Message: Hi, Iâ€™m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?

Hello, I'm having issues with gettin my account billing setup. I attached a credit card, and completed the Link signup. Not sure what I need to do next.

Hi there! It sounds like you're almost set up. After attaching your credit card, you should ensure that it's saved as your primary payment method. You can do this by accessing the Billing Section and checking if your card is listed as the primary method. If you haven't already, you might also want to add ad credits if you're using the Prepay option. If you're still facing issues, please let me know more details so I can assist further!
I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away.
I need to apply to "Add ad credits"

To become eligible to add ad credits, your account must complete and pass business verification, and accumulate over $5,000 in spend. Additionally, you'll need to establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality for you. If you have any questions or need assistance with this process, feel free to reach out!
